## Analytics & Tracking

### Metrics to Track
| Metric | Source | Frequency |
|--------|--------|-----------|
| Unique visitors | Google Analytics | Weekly |
| Page views by page | Google Analytics | Weekly |
| Traffic sources | Google Analytics | Weekly |
| Job views | ATS | Weekly |
| Applications by source | ATS | Weekly |
